## 🚀 STEP 3 — Fix admin.php Authentication

Your `admin.php` currently uses wrong session keys. Open `admin-auth-fix.php` and replace the **top PHP block** (from `<?php session_start()` through the role check) in `admin.php`.

**Root cause:** `login.php` sets `$_SESSION['user_role']` but `admin.php` checks `$_SESSION['user_name']` and role `'Administrator'` instead of `'Admin'`.

Also fix all JavaScript `fetch()` calls for approve/reject to use `FormData`:
```javascript
// WRONG (causes Network Error):
fetch('api/approve_farm.php', {
    method:'POST',
    headers:{'Content-Type':'application/json'},
    body: JSON.stringify({farmId: id})
})

// CORRECT:
const fd = new FormData();
fd.append('action', 'approve_farm');
fd.append('farm_id', id);
fetch('admin.php', {method:'POST', body:fd})
    .then(r=>r.json())
    .then(data => { if(data.success) location.reload(); });
```

---

