## 🐛 Common Errors Fixed

| Error | Cause | Fix |
|-------|-------|-----|
| Network Error on approve/reject | JS sends JSON but PHP expects POST form | Use `FormData` in fetch calls |
| Login redirects to index.php | Session key mismatch (`user_name` vs `user_role`) | Use auth fix files |
| Register shows "Pending" immediately | No email verification step | Fixed in new `register-form.php` |
| Chat not loading | `chat_messages` table didn't exist | Run new `database.sql` |
| Farm edit "Database error" | Mixed PDO/mysqli or wrong column names | All APIs now use PDO consistently |
| `updatedAt` column not found | Schema was incomplete | New SQL adds all missing columns |

